---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import ImageText from '../../components/ImageText.astro';
import BookingCTA from '../../components/BookingCTA.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Are you planning an event?"
	description="Running analysis, strength and conditioning and shoe management, get your event preparation right from the beginning."
>
	<PageHero
		title="Are you planning an event?"
		breadcrumb="Are you planning an event?"
	/>

	<ImageText
		image="/cycling.jpg"
		imageAlt="Cyclist preparing for an event"
	>
		<p>Marathon, half, London to Brighton cycle ride? Make sure you get it right to start with. A running analysis shows you how you run, which muscles are important for you to target in your strength and conditioning program and which could break down if you don't. Shoe management is crucial along with the right number or rest, running or cycling and strength sessions.</p>
		<p>We help you invest in yourselves to ensure that you get this right from the beginning and really enjoy the fitness, and achieving the goal.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<BookingCTA />
</Layout>
